# Core rules

RULE: use uv
RULE: keep reusable code in src/
RULE: write tests
RULE: run ruff, mypy and pytest
RULE: do not hardcode secrets
RULE: prefer typed, small, testable functions
RULE: keep IO separate from pure logic where practical
RULE: notebooks are for exploration only; reusable logic lives in `src/`
RULE: all filesystem paths must be imported from `{{ package_name }}.paths`
RULE: all configuration values must be imported from `{{ package_name }}.settings`

